        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9528a101-c1f3-43a2-a54a-10a310116d28">
                Mr. Bing
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9528a101-c1f3-43a2-a54a-10a310116d28" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-05/debates/f05b7819-b2e3-4b40-a364-f2d9a0b2ac04/GovernmentBusiness(Arrangements)#contribution-9528a101-c1f3-43a2-a54a-10a310116d28">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It seems to me that hon. Members are all very observant in picking out the right hon. Gentleman who would be most likely to give them a favourable introduction in that quarter. Those who have made such an approach are to be commended on their good sense in seeking an introduction—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9528a101-c1f3-43a2-a54a-10a310116d28" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
