        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-eecff9a7-c635-4adb-95ce-90f4c6755e81">
                Mr. Turner-Samuels
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eecff9a7-c635-4adb-95ce-90f4c6755e81" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-05/debates/f05b7819-b2e3-4b40-a364-f2d9a0b2ac04/GovernmentBusiness(Arrangements)#contribution-eecff9a7-c635-4adb-95ce-90f4c6755e81">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What I said was that laws were passed through another place, and when they came to be considered in the House of Commons we were gagged and not allowed to say a word about them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-eecff9a7-c635-4adb-95ce-90f4c6755e81" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-05/debates/f05b7819-b2e3-4b40-a364-f2d9a0b2ac04/GovernmentBusiness(Arrangements)#contribution-eecff9a7-c635-4adb-95ce-90f4c6755e81">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
