                Mr. Lennox-Boyd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8bbcd9ac-5242-4939-8690-8b2ce93b9133" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-05-05/debates/f05b7819-b2e3-4b40-a364-f2d9a0b2ac04/GovernmentBusiness(Arrangements)#contribution-8bbcd9ac-5242-4939-8690-8b2ce93b9133">
